text: Imangulovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Imangulovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 861 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 5 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Imangulovo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
